The SANY Group invested 15 billion yuan to develop industrial projects such as the smart steel production, smart petroleum equipment, regional research and development centers (headquarters), and a secondhand engineering machinery vehicle market in Zhuzhou; it is estimated that the annual comprehensive output value will exceed 200 billion yuan.
